++ Softwate Asset Tracking

SAT is a form of AssetTracking for [Applications] assets.

[Fields] recorded include:
    * licensing types
    * versions
    * prices
    * transferability
    * date purchased/last renewed

++Uses
    * aids moving to a different platform
    * determining licenses, eg, all open source or non-commercial
    * tracking licenses expiry
    * determining what licenses exist and how many installations allowable
    * calculate software costs per machine,
     * originally proposed to detect piracy 


